00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] Već na prvom poradu će da naći.

391
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tako će.

392
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] Srećite.

393
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] Osjetite.

394
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte.

395
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] Osjetite.

396
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mirni se Boga.

397
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] A On je tak vam da te doista.

398
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Prisnate.

399
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kada ga inakon osjetiš i okus je.

400
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] On da ti cijeli život.

401
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli te život drži.

402
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] I jedna četvijača.

403
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] Možda smo nekad opusili.

404
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] Boljevi svrti.

405
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] O, Bože.

406
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ja ne zudijem paola.

407
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je rekao da je njemu smrdo bitra.

408
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da.

409
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] Okusio Boga.

410
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Žive Boga.

411
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:33,960
[UNKNOWN] Žive Boga.

412
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je njemu smrto bitra.

413
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zato se nisu boljali svete.

414
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] Siti buđenici.

415
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] I današnog dva, Natalisa.

416
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] Koji je bio rogo.

417
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je postao papa.

418
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] I evo.

419
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] Žive je i tako.

420
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] Grosno smerio.

421
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] Bacio su da to z prozor.

422
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je nije u planama.

423
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] Trebao je živjeti rediče.

424
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] Neko on je ženio istinu djeve.

425
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] Evo dragio mladi.

426
00:16:58,960 --> 00:16:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] Prijatelji.

427
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] Draga braća i sestre.

428
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubina i Boženjecu.

429
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dojstaj.

430
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] Okusio otvorni srce Bogu.

431
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da Bóg potapne tvoje srce.

432
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tvoje duši.

433
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] Bóg je živjeti.

434
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dojstaj Bogu živjeti.

435
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] I on je čekaj.

436
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaj tak otvorni chudu.

437
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] Njego srce je otvorno,

438
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ti moglo uči.

439
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

